&lt;h3&gt;Disaster Recovery, because you have to consider the effects of a catastrophe.&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
Disaster recovery is essential risk mitigation.  What if a burst pipe from the office above leaks into the server room?  Just like buildings insurance, you don&rsquo;t want to fixate on it, but you have to have a plan in place against the kind of catastrophe which can destroy business critical data held on your machines.  
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
The good news is that our Kaseya backup system is cost-effective, and with it&rsquo;s disk imaging approach, will enable a restoration onto completely blank hardware in under an hour.  
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
This will ensure your business can keep running smoothly, so all you&rsquo;ll need to worry about is clearing up, and not how you&rsquo;re going to run your business in the absence of everything you need to know about it.  
